 BRIEF_10_missionNotes {
  coords 3110.753 10.001 3027.79
  m_sTitle "VI. Mission notes:"
  m_sDescriptionLayout "{E7AB311330BF986C}worlds/Perfk/UI/MissionDescription/DescriptionEditableScrollable_size18.layout"
  m_sTextData "<h2>Mission Intent</h2>"\
  "The objective is to rescue as many personnel (Player and AI) and vehicles from the ANA platoon as possible and return them safely to FOB Thunderbolt."\
  ""\
  "<h2>Setup timer</h2>"\
  "5 min for US. ANA should expect combat within 3-5 min"\
  ""\
  "<h2>Mission Status</h2>"\
  "Interacting with the flagpole in FOB Thunderbolt will provide you with a status of how many wounded and vehicles that were rescued. (GM or Command can press this at the end)"\
  ""\
  "<h2>Blufor Victory</h2>"\
  "Mission is considered a success if convoy personnel and vehicles are returned to FOB Thunderbolt."\
  ""\
  "<h2>Blufor Defeat</h2>"\
  "85% casualties. A mesage will appear and admin is expected to call the mission if blufor is unable to accomplish the mission."\
  ""\
  "<h2>Timelimit of 60 min. A message will appear and admin can call </h2>"\
  ""\
  "Admin is expected to call the mission. But should allow for firefights to end or if the convoy is close to FOB Michigan, then let the players end the mission using the flag pole to get stats"\
  ""\
  "<h2>This mission utilizes the standard (vanilla) Arma vehicle repair system:</h2>"\
  "To repair a vehicle, position the repair truck within 7 meters of the damaged vehicle."\
  ""\
  "Retrieve a wrench from the repair truck’s inventory."\
  ""\
  "Approach the vehicle and look directly at the specific part you wish to repair (such as the engine or tires)."\
  ""\
  "<h2>AI Medical Treatment</h2>"\
  "There are AI in downed but stable condition at the convoy location. These MUST NOT BE GIVEN SALINE or other treatment that will cause them to wake up. As they will act as stupid AI and run all over the place. Load them into the QRF vehicles and get them back to base where they will be counted for the end condition. Note their bleed setting have been changed and are therefore unlikely to die."\
  ""\
  "<h2>Fire Teams are assigned colors prestart</h2>"\
  "Alpha = RED"\
  "Bravo = BLUE"\
  ""\
  "<h2>Game Mastering</h2>"\
  "AI may get stuck outside buildings; Game Masters are authorized to reposition or spawn additional AI if the mission becomes too easy for the players."\
  ""\
  "Maintain balance and challenge, but ensure the mission remains fair and engaging."\
  ""\
  ""\
  "<h2>Mission by Perfk</h2>"\
  "Last updated: 2027-09-15"\
  ""
  m_bEmptyFactionVisibility 1
  m_bShowForAnyFaction 1
  m_iOrder 10
 }
